# FILE: halabAcademy/halabAcademy.desc
# ROLE: Skill Acquisition & Course Discovery Hub
# ROUTE: /academy
# ACCOUNT: All account types can browse — enrollment open to all
# THEME: Dark · grid catalog · gold borders for university-native content

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- PAGE BG: dot-bg pattern + subtle indigo glow top-center
- SECTION HEADERS: section-label pill + h2 (gradient-text on key word) + subtitle
- CARDS: bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl · hover:border-[#6366F1]/30

## 1. DYNAMIC BRANCH NAV (Sub-Header)
- STYLE: horizontal flex · overflow-x-auto · no-scrollbar
- BRANCH PILLS: rounded-full · bg-[#0F1828] · border · text-[#94A3B8]
  - ACTIVE: gradient-bg · text-white
- BRANCHES: برمجة · شبكات · أمن سيبراني · ذكاء اصطناعي · هندسة عمارة · طب · قانون
- SIDEBAR TRIGGER: [⚙️ فلاتر متقدمة] button — toggles filter sidebar

## 2. FILTER SIDEBAR
- POSITION: slides in from end, backdrop-blur overlay on mobile
- FILTERS: مجاني / مدفوع · محتوى جامعة حلب · التقييم · المدرب · موصى به
- APPLY BUTTON: gradient-bg · full width

## 3. ROADMAP GATEWAY
- CARD STYLE: bg-gradient-to-br from-[#6366F1]/10 to-[#8B5CF6]/6 · border-[#6366F1]/25 · rounded-2xl
- PREVIEW: thumbnail of roadmap.sh with blur overlay
- ACTION: [🗺️ فتح خريطة التعلم] → new tab to admin-configured roadmap URL

## 4. COURSE CATALOG GRID
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 · gap-6
- COURSE CARD:
  - TOP BADGE: "🏛️ جامعة حلب" — gold/amber bg + border (university-native content)
  - THUMBNAIL: aspect-video · rounded-xl · object-cover
  - INSTRUCTOR: avatar + name + rating stars
  - TITLE: text-[#F1F5F9] font-semibold
  - PRICE: gradient-text "مجاني" or "25,000 SYP"
  - STUDENT COUNT: text-[#4A5D78] text-sm
- ACTION: click card → /academy/course/:id

## 5. ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT
- Guest/Student: can view catalog, click to enroll (login prompt if guest)
- Business (vendor/advertiser): can browse only, not enroll
- Business (freelancer): can browse and enroll (upskill use case)
- Admin: can browse + has hidden [+ رفع دورة جديدة] button
